Name: Custom Chobits Chii Ears
Short description: Custom Chobits Chii Ears | ANY COLOR
Description:
These adorable persocom ears styled after Chii from the anime Chobits are sure to be the perfect addition to any cosplay (or everyday!) outfit.
\n
\nAnd, yes, they do open! Great for adding wires/plugs for authenticity.
\n
\nThis pair of Chii style ears are made from lightweight EVA foam and attached to a flexible plastic headband, so they are comfortable to wear all day long! They are adjustable on the headband, so they can slide up and down to fit you, or fit with any wig. You can also take them off the headband, and attach them any way you'd like (bobby pins work well when attaching these ears to a wig).
\n
\nWig and wig head are not included. Also, my mannequin has a small head, so these will be a more accurate size on a real human. =)
\n
\n***********************************
\n
\nThis item is CUSTOMIZABLE. The ears pictured are black and white, but you may purchase them in any combinations of colors and designs!
\n
\nWhen ordering, in the Checkout Notes, please choose the following:
\n
\n-If you would like the ears to be an unusual shape (longer than normal, one side bigger than the other, etc.)
\n
\n- The design for the decal on the outside front and back of each ear. I've done circles, plus signs, hearts, and several other shapes from the manga and fan art. (You may also choose none, or let me know if you want anything specific!)
\n
\n- If you would prefer the ears were NOT attached to a headband, but to an elastic band or left loose (for attaching to a wig), please specify this as well.
